Privacy Policy
Last updated:
12/11/2024
1. Information We Collect
When you use Room Aura, we collect information that you provide directly to us, including:
Photos you upload for design transformation
Account information (email, name)
Design preferences and settings
Usage data and interaction with our services
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:
Provide and improve our AI design services
Process and store your design transformations
Communicate with you about our services
Analyze and improve our AI algorithms
3. Data Storage and Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. Your photos and design data are stored securely and processed using industry-standard encryption.
4. Your Rights
You have the right to:
Access your personal data
Request deletion of your data
Opt-out of marketing communications
Update your account information
